'''黄梅秤锤树'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Sinojackia huangmeiensis''}}）是[[安息香科|安息香科]][[秤锤树属|秤锤树属]]的落叶小[[乔木|乔木]]或[[灌木|灌木]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Deng |first1=Sha |last2=Wu |first2=Yanni |last3=Wu |first3=Kunlin |last4=Fang |first4=Lin |last5=Li |first5=Lin |last6=Zeng |first6=Songjun |title=Breeding characteristics and artificial propagation of 14 species of Wild Plant with Extremely Small Populations (WPESP) in China |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-03-20 |volume=28 |issue=3 |pages=385 |doi=10.17520/biods.2020045}}</ref>，是中国的特有植物。仅有1个野生种群分布于[[湖北省|湖北省]][[黄梅县|黄梅县]][[下新镇|下新镇]][[钱林村|钱林村]][[龙感湖|龙感湖]]附近。<ref name="biods.2019118">{{cite journal |last1=Wang |first1=Shitong |last2=Xu |first2=Yaozhan |last3=Yang |first3=Teng |last4=Wei |first4=Xinzeng |last5=Jiang |first5=Mingxi |title=Impacts of microhabitats on leaf functional traits of the wild population of Sinojackia huangmeiensis |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-03-20 |volume=28 |issue=3 |pages=277 |doi=10.17520/biods.2019118}}</ref>

[[叶|叶]]纸质, [[花|花]]两性,[[果实|果实]]卵形, 靠[[种子|种子]]重力传播繁殖<ref name="biods.2019118" />。

